{
    "abstract": "The SVCB DNS resource record type expresses a bound collection of endpoint metadata, for use when establishing a connection to a named service.  DNS itself can be such a service, when the server is identified by a domain name.  This document provides the SVCB mapping for named DNS servers, allowing them to indicate support for encrypted transport protocols. ",
